<hymn_number>124</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kei di'n sawltha leh sunni vak talo,
 Thimin ei bawm ie aw ka Hukdampa;
 Na gam lopi tun kal ka ngaklah ie.

[V2]
 Ka Hukdampa chu ka ngai na zen e aw,
 Na hehpihna chawnban in ei kaiin;
 Hukdamte lailenna gam ninnuom ah.

[V3]
 2. Van kawtthel a khun Belam No Aw chun,
 &quot;Ka cha, hungin na gitloh puokgik tawh;
 Hun na dawn ingka&quot; ti in ei sam ie.

[V4]
 3. Na hehpih zie leh Na lopi zie chu,
 Kuoa gen thei ding lei mihingte hin?
 Van mite'n le a gen zo thei puou hi.

[V5]
 4. Na lungkham Aw bawna lei a lin chun
 Na lopin tawh Na hungkit tieng leh,
 Lei leh van in hun thuok zo hiel puon au,
 5. Zie bang ni lopi chu hung tung in tin,
 Na melmate lauin kiling un tin,
 &quot;En tie ei Tanpa!&quot; tin kiko ung kau.</lyrics>
<title>Na Gam Ka Ngai ie!</title>
</song>